node.text:
Due to the recent rise in Covid-19 variants, Maison Premiere will now be requesting all guests to have a proof of vaccination or a negative Covid-19 test from within 24hrs of their arrival at our restaurant. 

We understand these are uncertain times, and we thank you for your patience and support in keeping our community and staff safe.

node.text:
We are excited to announce the annual return of our back garden at Maison Premiere! 

Lushly appointed with tropical plants and clinging vines from Louisiana and the Carolinas, it is a justly famous getaway from the sweltering New York summer. 

As always, our bar is first-come, first-served, and all other reservations are available @resy.

node.text:
Come visit our talented Head Bartender Steven Rhea @st.rhea this weekend behind the horseshoe bar. Steven has been with us since the opening of @sauvageny in early 2016, and has been instrumental in our cocktail development ever since. 

No matter how busy or slow, this smiling gentleman loves to put on a show, and his cocktails are pretty top-shelf, too.

node.text:
To the many who have come through our doors the past week, we thank you. The outpouring of love, support, and good tidings has been humbling and exhilarating, and we are thrilled to serve you once more. 

We are also excited to announce Maison Premiere is now opening reservations @resy! Before booking, please check our website for the most up to date menu and hours of operation.
